ProtoDefines:
. "Let $p$ be an odd prime and let $a$ be an integer. Set $$ 
   \left(\frac{a}{p}\right) = \begin{cases} 0 & if $\gcd(a,p) 
   \neq 1$ ,\\ +1 & if $a$ is a quadratic residue, and \\ -1 & 
   if $a$ is a quadratic nonresidue . \end{cases} $$ We call 
   this symbol the {\em Legendre Symbol} ."
